      "message": "[warning] Line 912: The text-change signal exposes `index` and `deleteLen` as signed 32-bit integers, while the corresponding edit API uses unsigned values. This makes the D-Bus contract inconsistent and can deliver negative positions/lengths to clients or truncate unsigned callback values depending on the generated binding. Please use the same unsigned signature as `editCollaborativeDocument`.\n```suggestion\n            \u003carg type\u003d\"u\" name\u003d\"index\"/\u003e\n            \u003carg type\u003d\"u\" name\u003d\"deleteLen\"/\u003e\n```",
